    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-10-04T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-10-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="756"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d756">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terrell</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Legation of the United States</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-10-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 4, 1894</hi>
                        </date>. (Received October 22.)</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 319.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge your telegram of
                    the 3d instant, in reference to native teachers in American schools in Turkey,
                    and the capricious arrest of naturalized Americans.</p>
                <p>I hope to succeed in enforcing your views. * * *</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">A. W. Terrell.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
